instructions: On your iPhone, open the Chrome app . At the bottom right, tap More . Tap New tab .
On your iPhone, open the Chrome app . At the bottom, tap Switch tabs . You'll see your open Chrome tabs. At the top right of the tab you want to close, tap Close .
On your iPhone, open the Chrome app . At the bottom, tap Switch tabs . You'll see your open Chrome tabs. At the bottom left, tap Close All .
On your iPhone, open the Chrome app . At the bottom, tap Switch tabs . You'll see your open Chrome tabs. Tap the tab you want to switch to.
On your iPhone, open the Chrome app . At the bottom right, tap More . Tap Reload .
